content:
House voting now on Senate-passed bills to revoke normal trade relations with Russia and ban Russian oil imports. 

Both just passed the Senate 100-0.

House voting now on Senate-passed bills to revoke normal trade relations with Russia and ban Russian oil imports. 

Both just passed the Senate 100-0.

The House will *not* vote on lend-lease for Ukraine before it leaves for the recess.

content:
Europe relies on Russia for about 40% of its gas needs, with a third of those supplies traveling through pipelines crossing Ukraine. 
Any sanctions on Oil by Europe will be dealt by Russia by cutting gas supplies to Europe.
